settings.title: Do you ship overseas?
settings.content: Currently no. However we hope in the near future to reach our overseas friends. Please stay in touch to be notified when overseas shipping becomes available.

settings.title: How long will it take to get my orders?
settings.content: It depends on where you are. Orders processed in Australia will take 5-7 business days to arrive. Delivery details will be provided in your confirmation email.

settings.title: Any question?
settings.content: You can contact us through our contact page! We will be happy to assist you.

settings.title: FAQ
settings.support_hours: Our customer support is available Monday to Friday: 8am-8:30pm.
